title: Cossacks: The Art of War [PL]
description: Cossacks: The Art of War is the add-on of Cossacks: European Wars and takes place in the late 18th century. Among multiple features, the add-on provides a map editor recording battles and replaying them. The multiplayer option is featured as well, which is enhanced by the official Cossacks ranking list, where players can obtain titles of honor and view details on battles where they took part in themselves.
